data.description: Explore this 2,400 sq ft brick ranch featuring 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Walk through the newly installed hardwood floors that extend into an open kitchen with updated cabinets and a new sink. The countertops are adorned with durable quartz, complemented by a travertine backsplash. Efficiency meets comfort with included appliances, even an oven doubling as an air fryer. A substantial pantry enhances storage, while the rear porch with a BBQ pit invites laid-back gatherings. The large 1 acre lot invites the party outside. Embrace the ease of daily living and make this residence yours today.  NOTE: Principals of the seller may share ownership in a licensed real estate brokerage.
